Mobile:
Heading      = text-2xl → 24px
Subheading   = text-lg  → 18px
Paragraph    = text-sm  → 14px
Buttons      = text-sm  → 14px
Small Text   = text-xs  → 12px
Hero Heading = text-4xl → 36px

MD (Tablet):
Heading      = md:text-3xl → 30px
Subheading   = md:text-xl  → 20px
Paragraph    = md:text-base → 16px
Buttons      = md:text-base → 16px
Small Text   = md:text-sm → 14px
Hero Heading = md:text-5xl → 48px

LG (Laptop/Desktop):
Heading      = lg:text-4xl → 36px
Subheading   = lg:text-2xl → 24px
Paragraph    = lg:text-lg → 18px
Buttons      = lg:text-base → 16px
Small Text   = lg:text-sm → 14px
Hero Heading = lg:text-6xl → 60px

XL (Large Desktop):
Heading      = xl:text-5xl → 48px
Subheading   = xl:text-3xl → 30px
Paragraph    = xl:text-xl → 20px
Buttons      = xl:text-lg → 18px
Hero Heading = xl:text-7xl → 72px

2XL (4K / Ultra Wide):
Heading      = 2xl:text-6xl → 60px
Subheading   = 2xl:text-4xl → 36px
Paragraph    = 2xl:text-2xl → 24px
Buttons      = 2xl:text-xl → 20px
Hero Heading = 2xl:text-8xl → 96px

Recommended Production Setup:
Hero        → text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl
Heading     → text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
Subheading  → text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl
Paragraph   → text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg
Button      → text-sm md:text-base
Small Text  → text-xs md:text-sm